      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m honestly a little sad to be letting this one go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been my absolute pride and joy, always kept tucked away in the garage and pampered with regular details. It drives like a total dream and is ready for your next big adventure. If you're looking for something that's been loved and cared for, this is the one! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
