      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Offering a superlative 2004 BMW M3, a collector-grade E46 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a factory 8,000 RPM redline. This example is mechanically flawless; the Double VANOS system has been meticulously serviced, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to ensure structural integrity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise shift throws, pairing perfectly with the M-Variable Differential Lock for optimal longitudinal traction. The exterior retains its factory-original paint depth with zero rock chips or clear coat failure, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple with no bolster wear. Riding on staggered Style 67 forged alloys, the suspension geometry is dialed to factory specifications, providing the telepathic steering response this chassis is renowned for. This is a turn-key, investment-quality icon for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
